      "cooked": "<p>Beji mune Kembrixhit. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=5\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> Kurse wikipedia eshte shume simpatike. Gjyshja ime shkruan ne te herepashere kur i mbaron leshi i corapes mes dy telenovelave turke. Thote se po shkruan ne te, historine e vertete te Varrit te Bamit.</p>",
